description:
Follow Josh Gates down to the ocean floor as he dives deep in search of sunken ships, plane crash remains, and long lost treasures.

About Expedition Unknown: 
Josh Gates investigates the truth behind the world's most iconic and captivating legends. Leaving no stone unturned, his adventures take him around the globe as he immerses himself in the core locales linked to each tale.

About Discovery:
Dedicated to bringing our viewers amazing stories and experiences from the world of science, natural history, anthropology, survival, geography, and engineering.
